# No environment variables required for production (Vercel).
#
# For LOCAL development only — point to your system Chrome so PDF generation
# works without the full puppeteer bundle:
#
# Mac:
# PUPPETEER_EXECUTABLE_PATH=/Applications/Google Chrome.app/Contents/MacOS/Google Chrome
#
# Linux:
# PUPPETEER_EXECUTABLE_PATH=/usr/bin/google-chrome
#
# Translation uses Google Translate's free public endpoint — no API key,
# no signup. If you want to switch to a paid provider later (Anthropic,
# OpenAI, DeepL) for higher-quality business Japanese, swap the
# implementation in src/app/api/translate/route.ts.
